@startuml Mode2_NML_Ops_Chatbot_System_Flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #0f1117
skinparam defaultFontColor #e0e0e0
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam ArrowColor #4fc3f7
skinparam SequenceLifeLineBorderColor #4fc3f7

skinparam SequenceDividerBackgroundColor #1565c0
skinparam SequenceDividerBorderColor #4fc3f7
skinparam SequenceDividerFontColor #ffffff
skinparam SequenceDividerFontSize 13
skinparam SequenceDividerFontStyle bold

skinparam participantBackgroundColor #1e3a5f
skinparam participantBorderColor #4fc3f7
skinparam participantFontColor #e0e0e0

skinparam actorBackgroundColor #1e3a5f
skinparam actorBorderColor #4fc3f7
skinparam actorFontColor #e0e0e0

skinparam noteBackgroundColor #12263a
skinparam noteBorderColor #1565c0
skinparam noteFontColor #b3e5fc

title Mode2 NML Ops Chatbot — Full System & Permission Flow

actor "User\n(Browser)" as User
participant "IDP / Cognito\nUser Pool" as Cognito
participant "ALB\n(HTTPS)" as ALB
participant "ECS / Fargate\n[mode2-ecs-task-role]" as ECS
participant "Lambda\nOTP Function\n[mode2-lambda-otp-role]" as Lambda
participant "DynamoDB\nChatBot-OTP-Verification" as DDB
participant "SES\nEmail Service" as SES
participant "AgentCore Runtime\n[mode2-agentcore-role]" as AgentCore
participant "Bedrock LLM\n(Claude Sonnet/Haiku)" as Bedrock
participant "Knowledge Base\n(S3 + Titan Embeddings)" as KB
participant "STS\nAssumeRole" as STS
participant "Target Account\nmode2-ops-role" as TargetRole
participant "EC2 / RDS\n(mode2-managed=true)" as EC2

== ① User Authentication (Cognito + IDP) ==
User -> Cognito : Login request (SSO via IDP)
Cognito -> Cognito : MFA / OTP email verification
Cognito --> User : JWT Token (1 hour expiry)
note right of Cognito
  Authenticated Role:
  mode2-cognito-auth-role
  → execute-api:Invoke only
end note

== ② Request Routing via ALB ==
User -> ALB : HTTPS request + JWT Token
ALB -> ALB : Verify Cognito JWT
ALB -> ECS : Forward authenticated request

== ③ ECS / Fargate — Chatbot Processing ==
ECS -> AgentCore : Invoke AgentCore Runtime\n(bedrock-agentcore:*)
AgentCore -> Bedrock : InvokeModel\n(Claude Sonnet / Haiku)
AgentCore -> KB : Retrieve relevant documents\n(Titan Embeddings + S3)
KB --> AgentCore : Return context documents
Bedrock --> AgentCore : LLM response
AgentCore --> ECS : Agent response with action plan

== ④ OTP 二段階認証 (EC2操作前の本人確認) ==

note over ECS, Lambda
  🔐 EC2/RDS の操作は必ずOTP認証が必要
  誤操作・不正操作を防ぐための安全装置
end note

ECS -> Lambda : OTP発行リクエスト\n(ユーザーメール, 操作種別)
Lambda -> Lambda : 6桁OTPをランダム生成
Lambda -> DDB : OTPを一時保存\n(有効期限: 10分, 状態: pending)

note right of Lambda
  ⚠️ 本番リリース前に必ず削除:
  print(f"Generated OTP: {otp_code}")
  ↑ ログにOTPが出力されるためセキュリティリスク
end note

Lambda -> SES : OTPメール送信\n送信元: no-reply-security@mail.nissan.co.jp
SES --> User : 📧 OTPメール受信

User -> ECS : OTPコードを入力・送信
ECS -> Lambda : OTP検証リクエスト
Lambda -> DDB : OTPを照合\n(有効期限チェック + 使用済みフラグ確認)
DDB --> Lambda : 照合結果
Lambda --> ECS : ✅ OTP認証成功 — 操作を許可

== ⑤ 別アカウントへのアクセス (STS AssumeRole) ==

note over ECS, STS
  🔑 ECSは直接EC2を操作できない
  STSで一時的な権限を借りてから操作する
end note

ECS -> STS : AssumeRoleリクエスト\n対象ロール: mode2-ops-role\n合言葉(ExternalId): mode2-chatbot-trusted

note right of STS
  操作対象アカウント:
  ・B2C       NonProd / Prod
  ・Internal  NonProd / Prod
  ・Gamma     NonProd / Prod
  ※ ExternalIdが一致しないとアクセス拒否
end note

STS -> TargetRole : Trust Policyを検証\n(呼び出し元 + ExternalId の確認)
TargetRole --> STS : 検証OK
STS --> ECS : 一時認証情報を発行\n(有効期限: 15分〜1時間)

== ⑥ EC2 / RDS 操作の実行と通知 ==

note over ECS, EC2
  🏷️ 操作できるのは「mode2-managed = true」タグが
  付いたインスタンスのみ（タグのないものは操作不可）
end note

ECS -> EC2 : EC2/RDS操作を実行\n(起動 / 停止 / 再起動 / 状態確認)

note right of EC2
  IAM条件キー:
  ec2:ResourceTag/mode2-managed = true
  → タグなしインスタンスはIAMレベルで拒否
end note

EC2 --> ECS : 操作結果を返却
ECS -> SES : 完了通知メールを送信\n(操作者 + チームに通知)
SES --> User : ✅ 操作完了メール受信
ECS --> ALB : レスポンス
ALB --> User : ブラウザに結果を表示

== CloudTrail Audit (all operations recorded) ==
note over ECS, EC2
  All operations (AssumeRole, EC2 Start/Stop, RDS operations)
  are recorded in AWS CloudTrail for audit purposes.
end note

@enduml
